column1: # The September and October 1939 figures are shown in brackets on the sheet without explanation, and have been omitted.
# The May, June, and September-December 1941 figures are shown in brackets on the sheet without explanation, and have been omitted.
# The January 1945 figure is shown in brackets on the sheet without explanation, and has been retained.
# The gauge was at Ashby Road until the end of 1924.
